# Databricks Runtime & Photon

- Databricks Runtime (DBR) — the cluster image: tuned Spark + Delta + libraries + OS
- Versioned releases; pick LTS (long-term support) for stable production
- ML runtime variant adds ML libraries and GPU support
- Photon — Databricks' C++ vectorized engine, a drop-in speedup for SQL & DataFrame work
- Transparent to your code — no rewrite; faster and cheaper per query
